# Purpose....: Reference snippet for BasEnv coexistence via .bash_profile
# Notes......: Add the bash block from this file to ~/.bash_profile AFTER the
#              BasEnv initialization line. Do NOT copy to ${ETC_BASE}/basenv.conf
#              or sid.<SID>.conf - those files use BasEnv's own custom parser
#              and do not support bash syntax (causes parse errors).
# Reference..: https://github.com/oehrlis/oradba
